  <entry>
    <title>第一篇博客</title>
    <link href="https://46fafa.netlify.app/2022/12/24/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <id>https://46fafa.netlify.app/2022/12/24/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</id>
    <published>2022-12-24T13:06:37.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-01-12T09:04:10.109Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h2 id="起因"><a href="#起因" class="headerlink" title="起因"></a>起因</h2><p>学校里某日，网上冲浪，偶然发现自己在用的<a href="https://limestart.cn/">青柠起始页</a>作者<a href="https://maorx.cn/">毛若昕</a>的博客<br><img src="https://img-1316473855.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/1.png"><br>逛了一圈,觉得很有意思,然后通过大佬的友链访问了许多大佬的博客,之后就有了自己搭建博客的想法, 但是由于懒惰🙄,一直没有动手.直到放假闲来无事,才想着来试试</p><h2 id="方案参考"><a href="#方案参考" class="headerlink" title="方案参考"></a>方案参考</h2><p><strong>视频教程</strong><br><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1qD4y1z783/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click&vd_source=258020edca69c60087ab3235f74cfbbe">爱扑bug的熊</a> 和<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1G84y1B7NH/?spm_id_from=333.788&vd_source=258020edca69c60087ab3235f74cfbbe">–Fomalhaut</a>两位up主的视频</p><p><strong>图文教程</strong><br>其中<strong>hexo+github</strong>部署步骤的图文教程参考<a href="https://www.fomal.cc/posts/e593433d.html">–Fomalhaut的博客</a><br>netlify建站参考<a href="https://blog.cuijiacai.com/blog-building/">爱扑bug的熊的博客</a></p><h2 id="效果图展示"><a href="#效果图展示" class="headerlink" title="效果图展示"></a>效果图展示</h2><ul><li><strong>使用主题<a href="https://github.com/theme-nexmoe/hexo-theme-nexmoe">Nexmoe</a>效果</strong></li></ul><img src="https://jsd.cky.codes/gh/46fafa/blog-img@main/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A24.png"  style="width: 400px;">]]></content>
    
    
      
      
